  "rawMarkdown" : "---\nsource: https:\/\/developer.apple.com\/documentation\/CoreText\/CTTextAlignment\/center\ncrawled: 2025-12-14T02:52:24Z\n---\n\n# CTTextAlignment.center\n\n**Case**\n\nText is visually center-aligned.\n\n## Declaration\n\n```swift\ncase center\n```\n\n## Constants\n\n- **CTTextAlignment.left**: Text is visually left-aligned.\n- **CTTextAlignment.right**: Text is visually right-aligned.\n- **CTTextAlignment.justified**: Text is fully justified.\n- **CTTextAlignment.natural**: Text uses the natural alignment of the text’s script.\n\n",
